'''''Yeelen''''' ( Bambara kuri "umucyo" / "urumuri") ni film yo muri [[Mali]] yakinwe muri 1987 iyobowe na Souleymane Cissé<ref>https://www.albany.edu/writers-inst/webpages4/filmnotes/fns05n4.html</ref> . Ifata amashusho mu ndimi za Bambara na Fula, kandi ishingiye ku mugani wabwiwe n'abaturage ba Bambara<ref>https://mubi.com/notebook/posts/more-than-a-malian-monomyth-close-up-on-yeelen</ref> . Nubwo ibihe bitarasobanurwa neza, birashoboka ko byashyizweho mu kinyejana cya 13 mu bwami bwa Mali <ref>https://www.jstor.org/stable/3820136</ref>, kandi ni inkuru yo gushakisha ubutwari irimo ubumaji no kuvumbura.<ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/shop/DVD/Yeelen_-_Brightness</ref>

Irimo Issiaka Kane nka Nianankoro, umusore [[Afurika|wumunyafurika]] ufite imbaraga zubumaji<ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/shop/DVD/Yeelen_-_Brightness</ref>. Niamanto Sanogo akina nka se wa Niankoro, ukurikirana umuhungu we binyuze mu bihugu bya Bambara, Fulani na Dogon byo muri Afurika y'Iburengerazuba akoresheje inkingi y'ibiti by'amayobera kugira ngo amuyobore. <ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/shop/DVD/Yeelen_-_Brightness</ref>

