== ibikombe ==
''Yeelen'' yahuye nitsinzi ikomeye, <ref>https://www.kinolorber.com/film/yeelen</ref> ahabwa igihembo cyabacamanza mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 1987 . Yatowe kandi igihembo cya Golden Palm umwaka umwe<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/yeelen-brightness/</ref>. Yatowe muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga muri Film Independent Spirit Awards<ref>https://transmettrelecinema.com/film/yeelen-la-lumiere/</ref> . [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oKz68TZ9U4I Umuhango ngarukamwaka wa 4 wo gutanga ibihembo byumwuka wakiriwe na Buck Henry - igitaramo cyuzuye (1989) | Filime Yigenga kuri YouTube] 

Ni mwanya # 94 mu ''Nganji'' kinyamakuru "The 100 Best Films w'isi Cinema" mu 2010. <ref>https://www.festival-cannes.com/en/films/yeelen</ref>

